"default","preview_text":"","reshipment_settings":"disallowed","content":"\u003cp data-pid=\"nRbm9RDJ\"\u003e因为那个人教了真正的屠龙术。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp data-pid=\"PnWkk2SS\"\u003e做皇帝，做老板，或者做一个具有独立人格的人，靠什么？其实就是靠屠龙术。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp data-pid=\"PEz6nBW2\"\u003e资治通鉴是什么？资治通鉴是部门经理教你做老板，部门经理知道怎么做老板？省省吧，你今天听了部门经理的话，明天公司就要倒闭。财务也不能做老板，也就是cfo出身管理公司的，只会把公司做的一塌糊涂。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp data-pid=\"qDe0GeEW\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e学资治通鉴做皇帝的皇帝一定是一个失败的皇帝，学资治通鉴做老板的老板一定是一个失败的老板。只有创业的皇帝才有可能成为成功的皇帝，只有创业的老板才有可能成为成功老板。\u003c/b\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003chr/\u003e\u003cp data-pid=\"FaWdMAbQ\"\u003e我发现有人以为我在过分贬低资治通鉴，其实不是的，资治通鉴只不过是不适合做皇帝与老板的教材。当然，如果你就是准备去给皇帝或者老板打工，那资治通鉴特别好，要认真学，毕竟高官与高管也都是人中龙凤。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"is_thanked":false,"is_nothelp":false,"voting":0},"is_labeled":false,"visited_count":62928,"favorite_count":236,"answer_type":"normal","is_navigator":false,"navigator_vote":false,"vote_next_step":"vote"},"brief":"{\"source\": \"TS\", \"type\": \"answer\", \"id\": 1905825538783810891}","attached_info":"","action_card":false},{"id":"121_1753854015.183","type":"feed","offset":121,"verb":"TOPIC_ACKNOWLEDGED_ANSWER","created_time":1753854015,"updated_time":1753854015,"target":{"id":"1930667951792591863","type":"answer","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/answers/1930667951792591863","author":{"id":"ac1610eff729d8dd5b4f6b8e25ab948b","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/people/ac1610eff729d8dd5b4f6b8e25ab948b","user_type":"people","url_token":"aaxin-67","name":"AAXIN","headline":"环境科学 生物质燃料 量子化学计算 多物理场仿真","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-d86c408715ed33d4c91b9588ad39bbfe_l.jpg?source=b6762063","is_org":false,"gender":-1,"followers_count":297,"is_following":false,"is_followed":false},"created_time":1753087109,"updated_time":1753091732,"voteup_count":3747,"thanks_count":91,"comment_count":494,"is_copyable":true,"question":{"id":"1930183103399325903","type":"question","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/1930183103399325903","author":{"id":"dca396e04fd8c9410e5dbe49a352ecee","url":"https://api.z